titleNullable: Sahara Crime Report News - Africa, Nigeria
descriptionNullable:
This dataset is a dataset of hand-picked news from the Sahara crime report, it has three columns, viz: the label, header, and the url of the news.

The labels are Rape, Arson, Shooting, Bribery, Murder and Theft.

The header is categorically the title of the news.

While the url is the url where the news is located
